# Dialog Display Standard

- Use the shared `Dialog` component for all dialogs.
- Dialogs are centered, with frosted overlay and bounded size (not fullscreen on mobile).
- Internal content must scroll inside a container and hide scrollbars (`no-scrollbar`).
- Borders should be subtle, especially under `niho` skin.
- Close actions in dialogs should use neon pink styling under `niho` (e.g., `niho-close-pink`).

Example:

```tsx
<DialogContent className="chatee-dialog-standard">
  <div className="max-h-[70vh] overflow-auto no-scrollbar">...</div>
  <Button className="niho-close-pink">关闭</Button>
</DialogContent>
```
